}
\details{
The initial development scope is limited to leakage protection,
role validation, feature provenance, group-aware validation
contracts, and reproducibility reporting.

The package does not treat gaze, pupil, or biometric measurements
as direct indicators of emotion, stress, mental state, cognition,
comprehension, personality, diagnosis, deception, or intent.
